.DT
set_save_dir
Disk World creator help
set_save_dir

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_save_dir -  This function gives the suggestion box a directory to write its  suggestions to.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_save_dir(string dir)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^string%^RESET%^ - dir The path of the directory to write suggestions to 
it had better not end in / or you will be sorry.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/misc/suggestion_box.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function gives the suggestion box a directory to write its 
suggestions to. Either a save file *or* a save directory is required.
or your suggestions will not save.  If both are set then the save file
will be used.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_save_file()

.EP

